snippet.textDisplay:
I am extremely angry at those ppl who are saying they are buying views. I find it so damn funny when their fav group cant make views , they pull out youtube changed the critirea , ads won't count blah blah. But suddenly they are denying the critirea change bcoz of everglow. Mam a rookie gg making you feel that much pressed. First of all , their company is big in China. Secondly , their debut song literally went viral on China tiktok. Bon bon chocolat stage almost 6M views which is huge for a rookie gg. Their lyrics video has 11M views. ( now don't tell me lyics video bought views Imao). Dun dun dance cover is already surpassing 1M views. The song came out like 4 days ago but all the big dance cover channels are covering their songs. Even their line distribution video has huge views. Their stage show of Dun Dun surpassed 2.3M views already , the most viewed stage show of that day.
N why you guys are saying the likes n views ain't balanced ? 1.3M likes aren't enough ? There are many western songs which has huge views but likes are not that much.
U guys gotta understand everglow is still a new gg. Some of are casual listeners of them. They need some to have a strong solid fan base like other ggs. N trust me their likes and views are very balanced. Not everyone hit the like button after watching video. Unless you have a die hard fan base.
Everyglow is growing. N their sales ! That are improving. Trust me their sales improved from their previous one. N k-charts !
